        <p class="story-quote-text">
          The U-M image collections has hundreds of images featuring ann arbor and university history. Although the images are discoverable through library websites, but there is no opportunity to engage with these historical images resulting in a static look and feel to the collections.
        </p>

        <svg width="28px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 28 20" version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
