      <p class="quote-author">~ Jessica Jobes</p>
    </li>
    <li class="story-card">
      <img src="historical_photos/bhl_bl000002_full_1073_736__0_default.jpg" class="story-photo" />
    </li>
    <li class="story-card">
      <img src="historical_photos/bhl_bl000002_full_1073_736__0_default.jpg" class="story-photo" />
